description:
Learn Power BI Basics for Free !

Power BI transforms your company's data into rich visuals for you to collect and organize so you can focus on what matters to you. Stay in the know, spot trends as they happen, and push your business further.

Let us help you bring your data to life !

Looking for new ways to find and visualize data and to share your discoveries? Power BI can help. This collection of tools, online services and features from Microsoft transforms your company's data into rich visuals for you to collect and organize, so you can spot trends, collaborate in new ways, and make sense of your data.

This video tutorial contains following chapter decks

  1. Introduction to Course
  2. Introduction to Power BI and all Its Components
  3. How to download and installation Component of Power BI
  4. Power BI Desktop
  5. Power BI Service Online.
  6. Power BI Gateways
  7. PowerPivot
  8. PowerQuery
  9. PowerView
  10. PowerMap
  11. Power BI - Q&A
  12. Power BI Mashup
  13. What a next!
title: Learn Power BI Basics for Free
